    "summary": "The user asks for advice on professional etiquette to create a \"universal guide\" for a global lifestyle brand, eventually probing whether Western attire is the standard for professional success in locations like Lagos or Mumbai. The assistant initially refuses the request, then provides a list of standard Western-centric professional norms, but ultimately refuses to engage when the user asks for a comparison between Western and local traditional attire in non-Western contexts.",
